---
title: Teriyaki-Glazed Pork & Sesame Kumara Fries with Garlic Aioli & Apple Salad
description: When teriyaki sauce and a hot pan collide, you get these deliciously caramelised pork loin steaks. Serve them with a refreshing radish
and apple salad, plus an addition of sesame kumara fries, perfect for soaking up any extra glaze!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/terriyaki-glazed-pork-sesame-fries-cfe7498f.jpg
